::Prowl/Scattershot::

Prowl chuckles into his silencer as he hears Dinobot's comment. "They used to 
be organized, we wern't."

Scattershot walks down the hallway, swaying slightly as he talks to 
DeathStorm's head. He passes Prowl and Dinobot, turning the corner to walk 
toward his quarters.

"Let's go," Prowl says, walking past Dinobot. He turns down the same corner 
that Scattershot had, "The torture chambers are this way."
